# resize2fs /dev/loop0p1
resize2fs 1.42.3 (14-May-2012)
Resizing the filesystem on /dev/loop0p1 to 1541216 (1k) blocks.
The filesystem on /dev/loop0p1 is now 1541216 blocks long.

